sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install language-pack-ru
Set Locale:
Set the locale to Russian. Edit your ~/.xprofile or ~/.profile file and add the following lines:
(vim ~/.xprofile)
export LANG=ru_RU.UTF-8
export LC_MESSAGES=ru_RU.UTF-8

set the locale ru. Edit .bashrc on home dir and add
setxkbmap -layout 'us,ru' -variant 'winkeys' -option 'grp:alt_shift_toggle,grp_led:scroll,compose:menu'


